common_pains: Insurance billing is the hidden time-killer in every practice I talk to
Patient no-shows cost practices $200+ per slot
Staff spend hours chasing down insurance pre-authorizations

process_hooks.scheduling: Most practices I talk to lose 10-15 hours a week just on scheduling back-and-forth
process_hooks.billing: Insurance billing usually takes 2-3 touches per claim before it's resolved
process_hooks.patient_communication: Patient communication is usually scattered across phone, text, email, and portal
